title: treatment of sleep disorders
comment: This is the only reasonable application of the implant in my opinion. To treat sometimes fatal sleep disorders.

title: reduced accidents
comment: Accidents are sometimes caused by sleepiness (e.g. traffic, work-related) so this could be reduced.

title: productivity
comment: The implant could increase productivity in work and education. However, this is also open to abuse.

title: powers itself
comment: this sounds good but it means the implant is having some interaction with other bodily processes which might not be good

title: Recreational misuse
comment: As in people staying awake to socialise, party etc. This might have long term health impacts

title: Hackers and other criminals
comment: Hacking into the implant to make people wake or sleep. Could be used for blackmail and murder.

title: reliance
comment: As in people become reliant on using the implant to sleep and can no longer sleep any other way
